title: HERE IS A WARNING
lyrics:
In his veins, his blood flow
To the centre of his soul
It boils into breeding
Warmth that needs receiving
Here is a warning for you

Falling out, falling out, falling out

Of love

Of love





To and from, high and low

Transient times, tidal flow

A strain on your body

Draining the soul



Here is a warning for you

Falling out, falling out, falling out

Of love



Here is a warning for you

Falling out, falling out, falling out

Of love



Rapids of blood will flow

Feeding the urge, he grows

Of all my desire

But our time is up now
